document.topic_text: Get It To Jail: Note: "It" refers to Hillary Clinton. This sub is for everyone who wants to keep Crooked Hillary out of the Oval Office. We welcome Sanders supporters whose own campaign and sub won't go negative on It, and we welcome Trump supporters who are already fighting It. Everyone else with at least half a brain who doesn't want another corrupt Clinton for President should agree Hillary Clinton belongs in Prison. Remember: Putting It behind bars is fun! AMA's: /u/nistauditor, cybersecurity auditor and consultant Rules: Don't fight the candidates still running against It. We're already fighting a significant evil here, we'll have to do it together. No trolling against the sub (but troll It all you want from here). No racism or anti-semitism. No concern trolling. Message the mods, not the mob, with suggestions for improvements. Don't ask for upvotes. Post content that deserves upvotes instead. No doxxing or brigading. Post screenshots from other subs, not links - make sure to hide any personal info. Don't advertise your sub by using "x-post from ...". We don't care. Guidelines: Please try to avoid being sexist. Refer to Hillary with gender-neutral pronouns: It and Its. Use sli.mg if possible; it's for the better of this prison. Have fun!
